{"tid":1163694,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple售後再三屌打三星","createTime":"2019-05-20T15:00:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T06:17:26.000Z","uid":109383,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"018eddd68fec4d2522c462fa5b9be4efe6764740","tid":1163694,"uid":109383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T15:00:58.000Z","msg":"Apple Watch Series 3 缺貨？維修時會更換成 Series 4？！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n消息指 Apple Watch Series 3 的存貨處於低水平，從一些內部人事得知，今天起若 Series 3 需要維修或更換可以 Series 4 來取代。Apple 已透過內部通告，知會 Apple Store 及指定維修商有關的安排。暫時未知美國以外的地區是否有相同的安排。<br />\n<br />\n其實 Apple 過去也慣常在產品存貨短缺時，以較新的型號代替舊型號。不過由於 Apple Watch Series 3 仍在銷售，令人意外為何已沒有充足的維修更換貨源。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然而，若 Apple Watch Series 3 真的開始短缺，那更反映 Apple 可能會在秋季推出 Apple Watch Series 5，而 Series 4 則降價推出。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebd054820db5df8b07536fd4651f6efdedfc7ae8","tid":1163694,"uid":9193,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T15:02:06.000Z","msg":"屌打左好耐...起碼唔會全球保養唔包香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"561b2b91c1c3f0972d7036936e4ebf18bdf8412f","tid":1163694,"uid":22362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T15:03:12.000Z","msg":"有冇咁正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4147a93937d7c06d42f1755287a98f82f9fe0d","tid":1163694,"uid":313,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T03:40:19.000Z","msg":"拎apple售後服務同d垃圾an廠比...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b47171305e6a1823d29e9be3eb723ed25559af9a","tid":1163694,"uid":11916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T03:50:14.000Z","msg":"慣例啦<br />\n之前整6冇貨會換過部新6S<br />\n依家廢咗少少 某情況會通知你有零件返貨再幫你整<img src=